{
  "stem": "15943.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not right at the beginning-- a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had opened schools for a while, and they even had high school level, college level.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't last too long because everybody had to go to factories and, and start working.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you recall any anti-Semitism when you were a school child?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the school directly, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to, to Jewish school, so there was no anti-Semitism there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the streets, first of all, the stores always would have signs, don't buy by the Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or a Jew go to Palestine-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], Jew go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would hear people being beaten up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes we could see-- if somebody went by, you know, if we-- most of the times we stayed-- lived in areas that was basically Jewish, but to go to school, I had to go into different areas.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you saw some hooligans, as we called them, you stayed out of the way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You would go off the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If not, they'll push you off the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We felt the anti-Semitism, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we're going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We started at age six, so I think we came, came across it one way or another because school starts in Poland early-- age six you-- actually, here we start at age six too now, yeah.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like sometimes, they would go someplace and say, you know, they pushed us off the sidewalk, the same things, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], which means an insult, Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Going into a store and they would shove him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
